Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.57,0:03:00.05,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,光男先生 早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.46,0:03:02.72,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上好 少住持
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.05,0:03:06.87,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千代婆婆 早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.61,0:03:09.13,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您總是這麼早呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.13,0:03:11.94,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,村子裡有著信仰
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.86,0:03:14.36,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,寺院有很多佈施者
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.95,0:03:16.59,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但畢竟是鄉下
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.62,0:03:19.23,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佈施的數量可想而知
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.97,0:03:23.06,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,若是沒有佈施者們笑著伸出援手的盛情
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.17,0:03:25.07,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,寺院根本無法維持
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.83,0:03:27.84,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.90,0:03:31.02,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.63,0:03:35.78,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.57,0:03:39.39,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,村子裡的人逐漸減少
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.61,0:03:43.80,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 大家今天早上也還是一如既往…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.81,0:03:46.87,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然而 我…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.73,0:04:00.08,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下一位 請進
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.71,0:04:10.10,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,安代護士 帶他去治療室
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.48,0:04:11.26,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…是
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.40,0:04:20.09,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,德次郎先生
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.37,0:04:24.75,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,尊夫人節子婆婆 在去世之前
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.77,0:04:26.98,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,曾說過夢到了奈緒小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.26,0:04:32.56,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…奈緒啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.33,0:04:36.59,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也夢到了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.26,0:04:39.07,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然還是奈緒小姐嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.48,0:04:44.61,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎 可不能洩氣哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.71,0:04:46.36,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,厚子女士
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.73,0:04:47.47,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.58,0:04:52.31,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我認為最好謹慎些 讓德次郎先生住院
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.83,0:04:53.42,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.33,0:04:56.03,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,德次郎先生
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.65,0:04:59.63,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不住院 哪兒也不去
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.90,0:05:01.73,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我必須保護好佛龕
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.30,0:05:04.34,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佛龕就由我來…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.79,0:05:09.27,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行 節子就算住院了也沒能救活
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.29,0:05:11.46,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且我還有佛龕和工作
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.59,0:05:13.74,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能讓家裡空無一人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.55,0:05:15.48,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們別管我
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.67,0:05:21.33,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,簡直就像是機械地重複著背熟的話
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.47,0:05:25.24,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是被奈緒小姐叮囑要這樣說嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.63,0:05:32.38,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之前出診去下外場的前田勇家時也是…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.71,0:05:34.98,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不去醫院
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.61,0:05:39.30,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然外子說過絕對不要請醫生
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.61,0:05:43.17,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是因為和父親走的時候情況相似 我很害怕…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.20,0:05:46.02,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,害怕得不得了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.18,0:05:50.80,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那些傢伙為了使我不能讓患者住院
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.80,0:05:52.40,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而開始讓他們這麼說的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.40,0:05:54.21,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,該怎麼辦…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.80,0:05:57.60,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敏夫
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.11,0:05:58.70,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,媽媽
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.28,0:06:00.67,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,緊急情況
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.06,0:06:04.87,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恭子昏倒在房間裡了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.02,0:06:07.72,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,信明
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.96,0:06:10.90,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要去探望德次郎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.91,0:06:11.42,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,媽媽
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.27,0:06:13.94,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.59,0:06:17.42,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說去探病身體會撐不住 打個電話就好…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.43,0:06:20.80,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要去探望德次郎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.04,0:06:22.39,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他卻說爬也要爬去
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.13,0:06:26.07,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要去探望…德次郎…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.45,0:06:25.24,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,信明
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.11,0:06:30.14,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住…住持
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.45,0:06:32.07,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,突然這是怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.86,0:06:37.76,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒怎麼
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.41,0:06:41.75,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要去…探病
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.47,0:06:44.02,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去探病
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.28,0:06:49.78,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恭子
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.38,0:06:57.68,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,紫紺 呼吸困難…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.61,0:06:59.24,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是他們幹的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.42,0:07:02.89,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這2 3天來 叫她也不見人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.97,0:07:04.62,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我就從外面進來看看
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.18,0:07:06.67,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為窗子開著
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.01,0:07:08.00,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後就…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.02,0:07:09.84,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,媽媽 叫武藤護士他們過來
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.06,0:07:11.05,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有 抬擔架來
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.23,0:07:13.75,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什…我才不去呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.96,0:07:16.94,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼我要做醫院打雜的人做的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.02,0:07:17.74,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快去
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.74,0:07:22.66,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你欠我一個人情哦 恭子
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.69,0:07:28.32,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說起來 最近恭子安分得古怪
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.49,0:07:33.29,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我曾想過他們為什麼對我們視而不見
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.39,0:07:38.97,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來是尾崎家已經對屍變者敞開大門了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.00,0:07:46.56,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,醫生 少住持的電話
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.07,0:07:47.98,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,靜信…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.20,0:07:52.02,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那之後再沒見過他
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.88,0:07:54.73,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在想來
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.39,0:07:59.32,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從那時起 就感覺兩人之間有了條奇妙的溝壑
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.83,0:08:02.00,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這就為您接通
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.10,0:08:04.64,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敏夫
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.10,0:08:05.60,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喲
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.20,0:08:09.27,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛才聽安代護士說了 恭子小姐她…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.09,0:08:11.50,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 是那個
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.13,0:08:13.38,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼會這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.95,0:08:14.63,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,情況怎樣
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.98,0:08:16.57,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不妙
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.94,0:08:20.91,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敏夫…你又在自責了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.67,0:08:23.70,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這說明我們也不例外
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.30,0:08:26.86,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後呢？你有事找我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.64,0:08:31.78,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其實…我爸說要去探望德次郎先生
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.57,0:08:35.23,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,似乎是從媽媽那裡聽說他生病了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.03,0:08:39.84,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後就給安森家打電話問可否去探病
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.49,0:08:42.14,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說是在醫院裡
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.51,0:08:43.33,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來如此
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.05,0:08:47.87,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過 你爸和德次郎先生交情有這麼好嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.18,0:08:52.57,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道 應該是老相識了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.33,0:08:57.68,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 因為安森家是管理佈施者的四大家族之一
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.10,0:09:03.54,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊 節子夫人負責管理女佈施者
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.88,0:09:07.04,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可能是擔心孓身一人的德次郎先生吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.78,0:09:11.05,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎 我想他差不多該到家了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.40,0:09:12.26,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打電話問問吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.00,0:09:13.50,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.46,0:09:14.96,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敏夫…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.78,0:09:18.88,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.44,0:09:20.94,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.67,0:09:26.84,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒什麼 不用我幫忙保護恭子小姐也沒問題嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.14,0:09:30.29,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 我來想辦法
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.81,0:10:02.21,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最好快一點
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.78,0:10:07.68,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我爸可能會來探望我的病情
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.72,0:10:11.22,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然我很想去你那裡…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.61,0:10:14.65,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是我動不了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.42,0:10:29.65,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即便事已至此 我仍在期待著
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.36,0:10:32.65,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小徹會改變心意 和我一起逃走
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.21,0:10:36.76,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.69,0:10:40.31,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒關係
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.25,0:10:55.91,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總覺得 我逃不出這個村子
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.26,0:11:00.94,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我有這種感覺…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.55,0:11:11.12,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,水？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.19,0:11:20.46,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 是眼淚
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.75,0:11:25.85,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是沒有體溫的吸血鬼的冰冷眼淚
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.88,0:11:31.25,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梓 喂 梓
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.75,0:11:34.26,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去哪裡了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.46,0:11:42.73,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我看到夏野死了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.55,0:11:45.32,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個村子我也呆不下去了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.05,0:11:48.80,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我對你 對這個村子 都受夠了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.19,0:11:51.01,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再見 梓
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.20,0:11:54.54,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梓 不在嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.58,0:12:01.71,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這玩笑可不好笑…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.23,0:12:40.98,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.65,0:12:47.63,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.62,0:12:54.93,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 早上好…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.45,0:12:58.88,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鶴見先生…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.90,0:13:03.91,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鶴見似乎臉色很差 就讓他先回去了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.91,0:13:05.91,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,昨天明明還很精神呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.91,0:13:08.76,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不會得了什麼怪病吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.76,0:13:11.67,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別這麼說啊 光男
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.48,0:13:16.17,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老實說 我也很害怕…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.69,0:13:19.49,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總覺得發生了什麼很嚴重的事…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.62,0:13:22.49,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是 就算想逃
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.76,0:13:25.56,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為我是村裡土生土長的 也無處可去
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.46,0:13:30.87,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了好了 要是你離開了寺廟 誰來做弔唁呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.97,0:13:33.58,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.50,0:13:38.38,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了 說起來 好像新開了一家殯儀館
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.74,0:13:40.04,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,殯儀館？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.21,0:13:43.36,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是在上外場的宏兼家的木工店那裡
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.81,0:13:45.99,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是最近搬走了空著嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.19,0:13:47.73,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,殯儀館就建在那裡
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.17,0:13:50.20,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然是因為死人太多了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.71,0:13:52.78,note,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}（江渕診所）
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.59,0:13:52.49,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還開了一家新診所
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.86,0:13:56.12,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唉 真的很想離開這裡…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.13,0:13:57.67,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,豈有此理
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.96,0:14:01.09,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算死再多人也不該冒個殯儀館出來
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.44,0:14:03.82,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,村裡明明已經有負責弔唁的了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.08,0:14:05.87,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真不像話 外面的傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.70,0:14:14.16,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,厚子小姐 淳子小姐 真抱歉 突然登門造訪
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.16,0:14:15.85,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪裡哪裡 我們才不好意思呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.12,0:14:18.50,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓住持特地過來
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.97,0:14:25.77,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,德次郎先生 我們來探望您了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.37,0:14:28.40,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為父親堅持要來
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.71,0:14:31.37,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.29,0:14:50.20,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.02,0:15:01.42,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兩人都沒有說話
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.25,0:15:05.01,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,簡直就像是為了訣別而最後一次見面
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.45,0:15:06.13,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,靜信
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.49,0:15:06.99,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.12,0:15:12.59,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,節子和幹康也是那副樣子嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.12,0:15:13.76,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.57,0:15:17.11,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這種狀況在村裡蔓延了？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.52,0:15:20.17,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我覺得是的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.75,0:15:21.52,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.16,0:15:27.56,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道 父親知道些什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.44,0:15:30.24,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 怎麼可能…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.01,0:15:49.02,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,混蛋 為什麼…為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.76,0:15:54.58,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有人在嗎 叔叔
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.58,0:15:56.58,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥的身體 好些了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.83,0:16:04.06,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼不開門呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.06,0:16:06.75,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,昭 這樣敲門很不禮貌的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.50,0:16:09.81,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒辦法嘛 人家不開
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.94,0:16:13.38,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叔…叔…？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.33,0:16:21.69,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天要製作圓桌 小出工房很忙
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.78,0:16:26.32,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我沒工夫應付小孩子 請回吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.38,0:16:28.81,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個…夏野同學呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.81,0:16:31.50,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂喂 別打擾他了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.06,0:16:38.05,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天早上這家前面停了靈車 運走了棺材
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.73,0:16:40.38,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定是有人去世了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.91,0:16:47.61,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.76,0:16:52.68,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果當時能賴在外面保護哥哥就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.11,0:16:55.04,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.27,0:17:01.76,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難得結城同學的父親理解了我們 還願意幫忙…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.55,0:17:07.69,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下來 要怎麼辦？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.39,0:17:13.88,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總之 先鎖好門窗吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.81,0:17:16.09,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,結城君不是也說過嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.66,0:17:19.40,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,絕對不能讓屍變者進屋
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.67,0:17:23.54,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鎖上門窗也是白費功夫
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.86,0:17:31.78,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是爸爸吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.10,0:17:38.62,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 雙休日也工作
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.29,0:17:43.16,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就不能別麻煩我在這種時候給你做飯嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.64,0:17:47.32,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有 每天都加班 到深夜也不回家
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.32,0:17:49.32,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,公務所那有什麼班可加啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.16,0:17:56.47,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,肯定和同事一起去喝酒了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.12,0:18:00.48,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,媽媽 我們要睡了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.48,0:18:01.85,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,窗戶 鎖緊了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.85,0:18:02.46,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,煩死了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.21,0:18:04.54,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你以為我是誰？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.87,0:18:06.04,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我又不是保姆
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.78,0:18:08.42,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對…對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.99,0:18:13.29,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別跟我道歉 你愛怎樣就怎樣吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.24,0:18:19.35,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 可別喝酒喝到去看醫生啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.66,0:18:20.85,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,開什麼玩笑
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.97,0:18:23.27,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你趕緊給我去睡
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.27,0:18:24.20,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.96,0:18:32.42,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,心情真好
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.21,0:18:35.51,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看到討厭的傢伙遭罪
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.51,0:18:37.69,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真開心
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.09,0:19:26.55,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說 年輕醫生的夫人 怎麼樣了？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.30,0:19:29.31,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,安代護士 你看到了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.66,0:19:30.83,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.90,0:19:32.88,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,昨天會診的時候我在旁邊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.72,0:19:36.10,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那種狀況已經是晚期了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.57,0:19:40.00,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呼吸微弱 出黃疸
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.00,0:19:43.46,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有DIC彌散性血管內凝血症狀
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.00,0:19:48.26,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,變成那樣 基本上已經無力回天了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.45,0:19:54.74,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是醫生還是想靠自己的力量延長夫人的生命吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.45,0:19:56.95,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剩下的就由我來
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.10,0:19:59.81,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,包括餵飯和換洗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.54,0:20:02.02,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不麻煩大家了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.14,0:20:04.75,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,醫生是這麼說的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.07,0:20:10.44,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他也是常人啊 意外的很有人情味兒啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.92,0:20:15.33,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了 阿律 你和工房的兒子關係不錯吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.44,0:20:18.51,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 說過幾次話
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.32,0:20:21.77,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,工房那好像死人了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.89,0:20:26.60,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道過世的是媽媽還是兒子
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.10,0:20:29.28,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽說殯儀館的車來了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.26,0:20:33.43,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 醫生
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.84,0:20:39.71,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,醫生 需要我們幫忙嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.02,0:20:41.74,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用 你們別管
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.68,0:20:44.85,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不必在心
